latestPosts.caption:
@arjunkanungo is Indian pop’s ambassador to the world. The hitmaker and entrepreneur is Rolling Stone India’s May 2024 cover star. 

The voice behind songs like “Ilzaam” and albums ‘Industry’ and ‘Industry2’ has now taken his ambitions into the music industry to new levels, stepping into an entrepreneurial role with his label One Mind Music (@onemindmusic) and making serious steps to become big in Japan. With a label branch in Japan and a technology company also set up, Kanungo is taking charge. He says, “I think it’s taken a lot of confidence for me to realize that my shit was good enough.”

Hit the link in our bio to read the full cover story and check out all the photos.
